'''浴鹽'''，又稱為'''精神性浴鹽'''、'''PABS'''<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Implications of Psychoactive 'Bath Salts' Use During Pregnancy|last=Gray|first=Bobbe Ann|last2=Holland|first2=Cindra|date=June 2014|journal=Nursing for Women's Health|issue=3|doi=10.1111/1751-486X.12123|volume=18|pages=220–30|pmid=24939199}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title="Bath Salts" Intoxication|last=Ross|first=Edward A.|last2=Watson|first2=Mary|date=8 September 2011|journal=New England Journal of Medicine|issue=10|doi=10.1056/NEJMc1107097|volume=365|pages=967–8|pmid=21899474|last3=Goldberger|first3=Bruce}}</ref>，在英國又稱為'''猴屑'''（Monkey dust）<ref>{{Cite news|title=Monkey dust "epidemic" causing drug users to experience violent hallucinations|url=https://www.newsweek.com/what-monkey-dust-bath-salt-mpvd-drug-causing-epidemic-violent-hallucinations-1068295|accessdate=17 August 2018|work=Newsweek|date=10 August 2018|language=en|archive-date=2019-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031184437/https://www.newsweek.com/what-monkey-dust-bath-salt-mpvd-drug-causing-epidemic-violent-hallucinations-1068295|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一類[[娛樂性用藥|娛樂性用藥]]之[[狡詐家藥物|狡詐家藥物]]的名稱。<ref name="DEA">{{Cite web|title=DEA: Chemicals Used in "Bath Salts" Now Under Federal Control and Regulation|url=http://www.justice.gov/dea/divisions/hq/2011/hq102111.shtml|accessdate=28 December 2013|archive-date=2014-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425083923/http://www.justice.gov/dea/divisions/hq/2011/hq102111.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Situation Report. Synthetic Cathinones (Bath Salts): An Emerging Domestic Threat|url=http://www.justice.gov/archive/ndic/pubs44/44571/44571p.pdf|accessdate=1 June 2013|publisher=United States Department of Justice: National Drug Intelligence Center|archive-date=2017-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170503191950/https://www.justice.gov/archive/ndic/pubs44/44571/44571p.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 此名源自毒販為販賣此藥物用浴鹽名稱模仿[[浴鹽|浴鹽]]性質，以達到使用者在用此毒品淋浴時，不知不覺產生興奮作用的效果。<ref name="CBC">{{Cite news|title=What are 'bath salts'? A look at Canada's newest illegal drug|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/what-are-bath-salts-a-look-at-canada-s-newest-illegal-drug-1.1143407|date=25 June 2012|author=Black|first=Matthew|publisher=[[Canadian_Broadcasting_Corporation|Canadian Broadcasting Corporation]]|work=[[CBC_News|CBC News]]|accessdate=28 December 2013|archive-date=2017-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171221203406/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/what-are-bath-salts-a-look-at-canada-s-newest-illegal-drug-1.1143407|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="spiller">{{Cite journal|title=Clinical experience with and analytical confirmation of "bath salts" and "legal highs" (synthetic cathinones) in the United States|journal=Clinical Toxicology|issue=6|doi=10.3109/15563650.2011.590812|year=2011|volume=49|pages=499–505|pmc=|pmid=21824061}}</ref><ref name="coppola">{{Cite journal|title=Synthetic cathinones: Chemistry, pharmacology and toxicology of a new class of designer drugs of abuse marketed as "bath salts" or "plant food"|journal=Toxicology Letters|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.toxlet.2012.03.009|year=2012|volume=211|pages=144–149|pmc=|pmid=22459606}}</ref> 白粉末、顆粒、和晶體外觀和[[硫酸鎂|埃普索鹽]]（Epsom salts，硫酸鎂的俗稱）相像，仔細注意會發現其化學性質有明顯不同。該毒品會常會包裝成“非人類食用添加物”喬過去迴避《[[藥物管制法|藥物管制法]]》。 此外，也有可能會使檢務人員錯誤標記成植物性食品、[[洗衣粉|洗衣粉]]、或其他常用的粉末性物質包裝產品。

== 歷史 ==
合成性[[卡西酮|卡西酮]]（Cathinone）如[[甲氧麻黃酮|甲氧麻黃酮]]（Mephedrone, MCAT），化學性質與自然生成的卡西酮相似，在1920年代首度合成。<ref name="coppola">{{Cite journal|title=Synthetic cathinones: Chemistry, pharmacology and toxicology of a new class of designer drugs of abuse marketed as "bath salts" or "plant food"|journal=Toxicology Letters|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.toxlet.2012.03.009|year=2012|volume=211|pages=144–149|pmc=|pmid=22459606}}</ref> 但直到2000年代才被[[非法機密化學|非法機密化學合成家]]發現具有對人體有興奮作用及可偽裝浴鹽性質後才開始成為狡詐家藥物，這些化合物在許多合法司法管轄區疏漏處下開始用來合成這些毒品。<ref name="hamilton">{{Cite news|url=https://www.vice.com/read/hamilton-s-pharmacopeia-455-v17n6|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111030023436/http://www.vice.com/read/hamilton-s-pharmacopeia-455-v17n6|archivedate=30 October 2011|title=Hamilton's Pharmacopeia. Mephedrone: the phantom menace|author=Morris|first=H.|publisher=Vice Magazine|date=5 April 2010}}</ref> 2009年及2010年開始有情報指出該毒品最初在英國和歐洲其他地區合成卡西酮類毒品濫用顯著增加，然後在美國一些州也開始濫用的情形。該毒品在2010年被發現在市場上以“浴鹽”之名吸引青少年和夜店玩樂者，知覺浴鹽化學性質不對販賣者向[[美國毒物中心|美國毒物中心]]報告後，美國當局於2010年開始關注。<ref name="spiller">{{Cite journal|title=Clinical experience with and analytical confirmation of "bath salts" and "legal highs" (synthetic cathinones) in the United States|journal=Clinical Toxicology|issue=6|doi=10.3109/15563650.2011.590812|year=2011|volume=49|pages=499–505|pmc=|pmid=21824061}}</ref> 在歐洲該毒品在網路販賣藥物主要類型中佔主導地位，但在美國主要是在小型獨立的藥品販賣店，或藉由非法買賣毒品的人士走私的地點進行買賣，如加油站和迷幻藥品店。在美國此毒品非法交易比[[香菸|香菸]]及酒精容易。

有通報指出其他數百個狡詐家藥物也以“浴鹽”之名或冒充“合法興奮劑”在市面上買賣，這些人工合成化學物質包括[[合成大麻素|合成大麻素]]和半合成物質如[[1,3-二甲基戊胺|甲基己胺]]（Methylhexaneamine, DMAA）。 開發這些藥物的主要目是規避受到法律對非法藥物的控管，從而使它們具有商標名稱之標記，但這也會構成藥品商標侵權的法律問題，可能引來更多持有該藥物商標的藥品商法律訴訟控告及消費者對該藥品認知的混淆。<ref name="McElrath">{{Cite journal|title=Experiences with mephedrone pre- and post-legislative controls: perceptions of safety and sources of supply|last=McElrath, K|last2=O'Neill, C|date=March 2011|journal=The International Journal on Drug Policy|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.drugpo.2010.11.001|volume=22|pages=120–7|pmid=21242082}}</ref>

在美國關於“浴鹽”的毒物的通知呼叫案量從2010年304件上升到2011年6138件，根據[[美國毒物控制中心協會|美國毒物控制中心協會]] （American Association of Poison Control Centers）統計 ，與“浴鹽”相關的通知呼叫案量有下降的趨勢，呼叫案量在2015年降至522件。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Bath Salts|url=http://www.aapcc.org/alerts/bath-salts|accessdate=18 January 2017|publisher=American Association of Poison Control Centers|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119053143/http://www.aapcc.org/alerts/bath-salts/|archivedate=19 January 2017|quote=In 2012, poison centers took 2,697 calls about exposures to bath salts with the number reducing to 998 in 2013. In 2014, there were 587 exposure calls with the number reducing to 522 in 2015.}}</ref>

== 藥理學 ==
在藥理學上，浴鹽常常包含卡西酮，一般是[[亞甲基二氧吡咯戊酮|亞甲基二氧吡咯戊酮]]（Methylenedioxypyrovalerone, MDPV）、[[亞甲基雙氧甲基卡西酮|亞甲基雙氧甲基卡西酮]]（Methylone）或甲氧麻黃酮等化合物構成；然而此類毒品的化學物組成非常多變，產品會標籤為相同的名字，並會包括額外的化學衍生物如<ref name="spiller">{{Cite journal|title=Clinical experience with and analytical confirmation of "bath salts" and "legal highs" (synthetic cathinones) in the United States|journal=Clinical Toxicology|issue=6|doi=10.3109/15563650.2011.590812|year=2011|volume=49|pages=499–505|pmc=|pmid=21824061}}</ref><ref name="prosser">{{Cite journal|title=The Toxicology of Bath Salts: A Review of Synthetic Cathinones|journal=Journal of Medical Toxicology|issue=1|doi=10.1007/s13181-011-0193-z|year=2011|volume=8|pages=33–42|pmc=3550219|pmid=22108839}}</ref> [[吡咯戊酮|吡咯戊酮]]（Pyrovalerone）或[[哌苯甲醇|哌苯甲醇]]（Pipradrol）。在歐洲該毒品成分主要以合成性卡西酮和甲氧麻黃酮構成，美國構成則以亞甲基二氧吡咯戊酮較為普遍。

關於浴鹽如何與大腦相互作用以及該毒品如何被[[人體代謝|人體代謝]]了解甚少。科學家傾向於研究浴鹽具有強大的成癮潛力，並且會提高使用者的對該毒品的耐受性。<ref name="coppola">{{Cite journal|title=Synthetic cathinones: Chemistry, pharmacology and toxicology of a new class of designer drugs of abuse marketed as "bath salts" or "plant food"|journal=Toxicology Letters|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.toxlet.2012.03.009|year=2012|volume=211|pages=144–149|pmc=|pmid=22459606}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title="Bath Salts" Intoxication|last=Ross|first=EA|last2=Watson|first2=M|date=8 September 2011|journal=The New England Journal of Medicine|issue=10|doi=10.1056/NEJMc1107097|volume=365|pages=967–968|pmid=21899474|last3=Goldberger|first3=B}}</ref> 該毒品的化合物和[[苯丙胺|苯丙胺]]（Amphetamine）同樣能造成使用者成癮，以提升的單胺類神經遞質類物質的濃度如[[多巴胺|多巴胺]]、[[血清素|血清素]]和[[去甲腎上腺素|去甲腎上腺素]]在[[突觸|突觸]]裡就能達到效果<ref name="Kehr">{{Cite journal|title=Mephedrone, compared to MDMA (ecstasy) and amphetamine, rapidly increases both dopamine and serotonin levels in nucleus accumbens of awake rats|last=Kehr|first=J.|last2=Ichinose|first2=F.|date=April 2011|journal=British Journal of Pharmacology|issue=8|doi=10.1111/j.1476-5381.2011.01499.x|volume=164|pages=1949–58|pmc=3246659|pmid=21615721|last3=Yoshitake|first3=S.|last4=Goiny|first4=M.|last5=Sievertsson|first5=T.|last6=Nyberg|first6=F.|last7=Yoshitake|first7=T.}}</ref>。但它們基本上與苯丙胺相比較不能跨過[[血腦屏障|血腦屏障]]，在[[酮酸|酮酸]]群化合物面前提升該毒品化合物的[[極性|極性]]。

== 用途 ==
浴鹽會被吸入、噴鼻、吸入煙、注射。所有有通報浴鹽的毒物控制機構特別建議千萬不要注射此毒品，因為這些毒品的包裝成分列舉不實，更別說一丁點劑量，所引起的副作用導致行為不穩定、產生幻覺和妄想。<ref name="emcdda">{{Cite web|title=Europol–EMCDDA Joint Report on a new psychoactive substance: 4-methylmethcathinone (mephedrone)|url=http://www.emcdda.europa.eu/attachements.cfm/att_102496_EN_Europol-EMCDDA_Joint_Report_Mephedrone.pdf|date=27 May 2010|publisher=European Monitoring Centre for Drugs and Drug Addiction|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110408215242/http://www.emcdda.europa.eu/attachements.cfm/att_102496_EN_Europol-EMCDDA_Joint_Report_Mephedrone.pdf|archivedate=8 April 2011}}</ref>

=== 酒精相互作用 ===
浴鹽常和酒精共同消費掉，使該毒品興奮作用和酒精引起的效果起交互反應。一項2015年研究專門顯示甲氧麻黃酮和酒精的交互作用，尤其是在精神興奮劑效果和加成得益方面。研究顯示低劑量非興奮劑毒品和酒精，會提升甲氧麻黃酮之精神興奮劑效果<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Alcohol enhances the psychostimulant and conditioning effects of mephedrone in adolescent mice; postulation of unique roles of D receptors and BDNF in place preference acquisition|last=Ciudad-Roberts|first=Andrés|last2=Camarasa|first2=Jorge|date=2015|journal=British Journal of Pharmacology|issue=20|doi=10.1111/bph.13266|volume=172|pages=4970–4984|pmc=4621996|pmid=26228024|last3=Ciudad|first3=Carlos J.|last4=Pubill|first4=David|last5=Escubedo|first5=Elena}}</ref>  。其效果例如：調停並提升多巴胺進入突觸接觸神經細胞，[[氟哌啶醇|氟哌啶醇]]（Haloperidol）也具有效果，但[[酮色林|酮色林]]（Ketanserin）就無效，會消珥掉酒精的增毒作用。
